Use Alexa to voice control your Unisenza products. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
1. Download our "Unisenza" app in app market, then register an account (or log in directly if you already have an account);
2. Configure our devices in "Unisenza" app and change appropriate name for your devices;
3. Enable "Unisenza" skill on Alexa app, you'll be navigated to the login page, follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
4. Tell Echo "Alexa, discover my devices". Wait for Echo to say "Search complete";
5. Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
Alexa, Change bedroom to 23 degrees / Alexa, Set bedroom to 23 degrees
Alexa, Change bedroom to heating / Alexa, Set bedroom to heating
Alexa, Change bedroom to cooling / Alexa, Set bedroom to cooling
Alexa, Change bedroom to off mode / Alexa, Set bedroom to off mode
Alexa, what is bedroom temperature?
Alexa, Raise bedroom by 2 degrees / Alexa, Increase bedroom by 2 degrees
Alexa, Lower bedroom by 2 degrees / Alexa, Decrease bedroom by 2 degrees
